Chloe Cherry’s anal abilities are top-tier and there isn’t anyone in the business better at making anal-themed porn than director/performer Mike Adriano. All of that results in Slut Auditions making the Top 5 in this countdown of the best Chloe Cherry smut. In a scene that spans more than an hour, Mike and Chloe engage in pretty much every form of sex that you can imagine and possible a few that you can’t until you’ve seen it done.

