2. Blind Surprise (2018) | Pure Taboo
10 Best Chloe Cherry Porn Movies - Blind Surprise

Blind Surprise probably represents Chloe Cherry’s most powerful role of her career thus far and she has the 2019 AVN Best Actress award nomination to prove it. Partnered with the always terrific Ricky Johnson, Chloe helps bring to life an incredibly twisted story that will likely leave most viewers shook. Probably better than any of her other work, Blind Surprise gives us the most complete look at what makes Chloe such a special talent. As an additional note, if you are looking to get this on DVD or streaming, you actually have to pick up Pure Taboo’s Mail Order as they package Blind Surprise with that as a “B side”.

